                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On March 22, at the meeting of the Ambassadors at Rome, Commissioner McCloy
                    reviewed the German situation and stressed the importance of maintaining the
                    position of the Western Allies in Berlin. For the summary record of his
                    statement, see <ref target="frus1950v03#pg_810">volume III, page 810</ref>.</p>
            </div>
